text: Valerie Mullins (born 17 January 1935) is a British gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:British female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Swansea
